Company Overview of Cogito Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cogito Corporation develops and delivers an artificial intelligence and behavioral analytics software solution that analyzes human voice and provides real-time guidance to enhance behavior. The company offers Cogito, a suite of solutions that analyze phone conversations and provide sales, service, and care management professionals with real-time emotional intelligence to improve sales results, deliver customer experiences, and enhance quality of care. Its suite of products include Cogito Dialog, a solution that provides real-time in-call analysis of telephone interactions with customers; Cogito Central, which enables continuous scoring of customer interactions for engagement and distress acr...
Cogito Corporation develops and delivers an artificial intelligence and behavioral analytics software solution that analyzes human voice and provides real-time guidance to enhance behavior. The company offers Cogito, a suite of solutions that analyze phone conversations and provide sales, service, and care management professionals with real-time emotional intelligence to improve sales results, deliver customer experiences, and enhance quality of care. Its suite of products include Cogito Dialog, a solution that provides real-time in-call analysis of telephone interactions with customers; Cogito Central, which enables continuous scoring of customer interactions for engagement and distress across an organization; and Cogito Companion, a smartphone application that continuously and passively collects data on activity, social interaction, sleep patterns, and mood. The company’s solution also helps enterprises enhance employee productivity and care for their customers by applying validated behavioral science through artificial intelligence and machine learning. It offers solutions to deliver enhance customer services, sales, and care management with real-time emotional intelligence. The company was formerly known as Cogito Health Inc. and changed its name to Cogito Corporation in March 2016. Cogito Corporation was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts.
