Product Description




Cogito enhances the emotional intelligence of phone professionals through behavioral change software. By applying validated cognitive science through artificial intelligence, Cogito analyzes voices within phone conversations, detects behavioral patterns and delivers live in-call guidance. The software automatically provides an objective, comprehensive and real-time measure of customer experience. Cogito is helping the world’s most successful enterprises improve sales results, deliver amazing customer service and enhance quality of care.




Whitepapers, Archived Webcasts and Sponsored Content






Leveraging the Power of Cogito to Improve Employee Productivity and Increase Customer Loyalty
Read about the key behaviors that lead to more productive employees and more engaged customers and how Cogito helps improve ROI metrics such as NPS, first call resolution, and average handle time.


Artificial Intelligence is Shaping the Future of Customer Experience
Read how Humana uses Cogito's AI software to transform customer and employee experience within the call center leading to improvements in customer satisfaction, employee engagement, and issue resolution.


Elevating Customer Experience with Real-Time Emotional Intelligence
Learn how Cogito helped one Fortune 100 health insurer reduce handle times, improve customer satisfaction, and elevate service delivery through real-time emotional intelligence.






